{"tid":2195183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"籌款不及對手拜登 川普：願意自掏腰包競選","createTime":"2020-09-09T04:14:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T09:10:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c52ac756b7b5788bfda1dbf2dc249858f0c7d144","tid":2195183,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:14:42.000Z","msg":"綜合外媒報導，川普團隊自2019年以來，已砸8億美金在競選活動，相當於對手拜登的兩倍多，鉅額支出卻沒有反映在民調。川普受訪時表示，願意自費競選，並強調，今年的總統大選是「美國歷史上最重要的選舉」，不管要付出多少代價都必須贏。<br />\n<br />\n川普團隊競選總幹事史泰平（Bill Stepien）8日在記者會上表示，目前正在謹慎管理預算<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n川普強調，不認為團隊目前有資金短缺的問題，但若是需要更多的經費，將會自掏腰包<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n根據知情人士表示，川普和團隊討論後，正考慮為競選活動投入高達一億美元的資金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3285964\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3285964&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwg8%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=d1a80397\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3285964&h=61597119\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3285964</a>"},{"pid":"667f2f7d2e8a729a4c8dd0560cbcb2097161502b","tid":2195183,"uid":12597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"侵都唔志在錢啦"},{"pid":"f922c0fbf5629c53d50e3fcf03409fcbec216c61","tid":2195183,"uid":127575,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"667f2f7d2e8a729a4c8dd0560cbcb2097161502b","tid":2195183,"uid":12597,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:19:14.000Z","msg":"侵都唔志在錢啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"侵侵都破產過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n錢對佢來講濕濕碎"},{"pid":"ec7c6d664d810daf4eae522c471a1732e4f768da","tid":2195183,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"20