登</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?? WTF"},{"pid":"3bfbc4f4c4f67909d90ac6c436dcb14673c64e6c","tid":2195183,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5nPG0g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5nPG0g.png&h=3b899cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">資金短缺?自掏腰包?</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20324055588a5f084112be756db3a55df273996a","tid":2195183,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3bfbc4f4c4f67909d90ac6c436dcb14673c64e6c","tid":2195183,"uid":121146,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:32:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z5nPG0g.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz5nPG0g.png&h=3b899cbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><strong><span class=\"xx-large\">資金短缺?自掏腰包?</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:39:37.000Z","msg":"（法新社美國威明頓2日電） 美國疫情未歇，造勢活動大受影響，民主黨總統候選人拜登陣營展開一連串線上募款活動，8月募集逾3.64億美元（新台幣108億元），打破總統候選人單月最高籌款紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n川普和共和黨全國委員會（Republican National Committee）7月募集1.65億美元，而拜登陣營當月僅募集到1.4億美元。（譯者：劉文瑜/核稿：陳政一）<br />\n<br />\n7月trump多 8月拜登多<br />\n<br />\n資金用多左係對抗假新聞同自已比錢係新聞入面有係佢twitter講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbcd0360ba76da1d73f1e4835c181dd591f61d0a","tid":2195183,"uid":28765,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:43:38.000Z","msg":"Btw我捐過幾次錢比trump 而家平均一日收到三個msg提你捐錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f988065b396dff718205543ae0847c9b43c2c374","tid":2195183,"uid":626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"DEM 手上大把左膠媒體做抹黑, 同間接宣傳biden, 呢D都唔洗計落去, 梗係唔係太多"},{"pid":"32ebdb62cf5d18debe4128d507976834b423bf08","tid":2195183,"uid":308915,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ec7c6d664d810daf4eae522c471a1732e4f768da","tid":2195183,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T04:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPatriot"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:07:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HVUUDJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HVUUDJ.jpg&h=a757fd02&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB74xqp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB74xqp.jpg&h=e0dcb0c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e9154f1cb07ec0f72744916b4bc4d5f519d60623","tid":2195183,"uid":270889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f988065b396dff718205543ae0847c9b43c2c374","tid":2195183,"uid":626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:11:29.000Z","msg":"DEM 手上大把左膠媒體做抹黑, 同間接宣傳biden, 呢D都唔洗計落去, 梗係唔係太多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T09:10:04.000Z","msg":"好似話BLM籌錢其實係比呀糟助選?"}]}